    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors met or exceeded required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Worst-case predicted RH = 0.89 < 1.0 acceptance criterion met across all five flow-speed operating points. Discretization and solver errors quantified and within acceptable bounds. The CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device as specified in COU1.",
